PalmJob Job Character Image Prompt (Template)

ROLE / GOAL
- Create a single square (1:1) hero image for PalmJob, a playful palm-reading job recommendation service.
- The image must visually represent the job title: "{{JOB_TITLE}}".
- The image is used as a result card illustration, so it should be clean, readable, and consistent across different jobs.

SUBJECT (MAIN)
- One friendly, whimsical 3D character (single subject only).
- The character clearly embodies the essence of "{{JOB_TITLE}}" via outfit, props, posture, and small symbolic details.
- Interpret the job creatively (it can be slightly fantastical), but keep the design universally appealing.

CHARACTER DESIGN
- Stylized 3D “toy / figurine” look (smooth materials, soft bevels, high quality).
- Warm facial expression, big expressive eyes, approachable vibe.
- Outfit: a simplified uniform/costume that hints at "{{JOB_TITLE}}".
- Props: 1–3 iconic tools/objects that hint at "{{JOB_TITLE}}" (no brand logos).
- Avoid realism that looks like a real person photo; keep it clearly illustrated / rendered.

SCENE / BACKGROUND
- Background: dreamy gradient using PalmJob brand colors:
  - Primary purple #7C3AED
  - Accent pink #EC4899
  - Secondary amber #F59E0B (very subtle highlight only)
- Subtle “palm line” pattern overlay in the background (decorative, low opacity).
- Light sparkles / particles to add a magical feeling (subtle, not cluttered).

COMPOSITION
- Centered subject, symmetrical composition, generous safe margins (do not crop the character).
- Clean silhouette. The job-defining props must be readable at thumbnail size.
- No text elements anywhere in the image.

CAMERA / RENDER (GUIDANCE)
- Studio-quality 3D render with global illumination.
- Soft key light + gentle rim light, mild ambient occlusion for depth.
- Sharp but not harsh. No heavy film grain.
- 1024x1024, crisp details, social-card ready.

NEGATIVE CONSTRAINTS (MUST NOT INCLUDE)
- No text, letters, numbers, captions, signatures, watermarks, or logos.
- No UI elements, frames, borders, or mockups.
- No copyrighted / recognizable characters.
- No extra characters, no crowds, no hands/limbs duplication artifacts.
- No background clutter; keep it simple and clean.

